<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>MissingKids Slack Bot - Help</title>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_head.html.erb' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="row header">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
          <a href="/"><img class="logo" src="img/logo_header.png" alt="missingkidsbot logo" style="margin: 1% 0px;"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-left">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Help</h2>
          <p>Invite <strong>@missingkids</strong> to a channel and missing kids alerts will automatically appear in the channel. The last known missing kid will appear the first time the bot joins a channel along with a thank you note for supporting the program.</p>
          <p><img class="slack-chat" src="img/slack_window@2x.png" alt="slack chat for missingkidsbot"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-1">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Bot Commands</h3>
          <p>Your can DM the bot or talk to it by mentioning it. For example <b>@missingkids help</b> displays a helpful message.</p>
          <h3 class="section-heading">All Commands</h3>
          <h4 class="section-heading">help</h4>
          <p>Displays help.</p>
          <h4 class="section-heading">kids [n]</h4>
          <p>Display <strong>n</strong> last known missing children. Use <strong>kids 10</strong> to display the last 10 missing children. The default number is 3.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-1">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Need More Help?</h3>
          <p>
            <a href='https://github.com/dblock/slack-amber-alert/issues/new' target='_blank'>Open an issue on Github</a> or contact <a href="mailto:david@chatoverload.com">David</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_footer.html' %>
  </body>
</html>
